collectors.titleDetails: (2 total Queries, 2 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `id`, `model`, (SELECT nilai FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = produk.id AND fkKriteria = 10) AS Fungsi, (SELECT nilai FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = produk.id AND fkKriteria = 11) AS Harga, (SELECT nilai FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = produk.id AND fkKriteria = 12) AS Kapasitas, (SELECT nilai FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = produk.id AND fkKriteria = 13) AS Ukuran, (SELECT nilai FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = produk.id AND fkKriteria = 14) AS DayaListrik, (SELECT nilai FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = produk.id AND fkKriteria = 15) AS Merek FROM `produk` WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = `produk`.`id` AND `fkKriteria` = 10 AND `nilai` = 'otomatis') AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = `produk`.`id` AND `fkKriteria` = 11 AND `nilai` < 3000000) AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM fitur WHERE fkProduk = `produk`.`id` AND `fkKriteria` = 12 AND `nilai` < 9)
